Metadata: THREE PUBLICATIONS RELATED TO ECHO INTEGRATION FROM THE WASHINGTON SEA GRANT MARINE ACOUSTICS PROGRAM
CONTAINS ENTRIES WASHU-J-71-001 -003 (no longer catalogued with these numbers but still listed in the old indexes)

Three publications related to echo integration from the Washington Sea Grant Marine Acoustics Program: WSG 71-2: A simplified analysis of the statistical characteristics of the fish echo integrator. WSG 71-3: The variance of fish population estimates using an echo integrator. WSG 71-4: Derivation and numerical evaluation of a general variance expression for fish population estimates using an echo integrator.
